{"tid":1886130,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做個統計 真係冇人寫讚揚信比港台？","createTime":"2020-02-18T17:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T16:29:58.000Z","uid":315647,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ed891163f2489e6631e19f75aaa663a0f4587ef2","tid":1886130,"uid":315647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T17:53:44.000Z","msg":"收得個200投訴就大肆宣揚<br />\n我就唔係好信冇人寫讚揚信比港台<br />\n<br />\n不如做個統計 <br />\n寫左信既留個名 聽晚12點截數 <br />\n如果讚既多過踩既係米代表商經局好既扮聽唔到？！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">利申純好奇加不齒高汁既頭條新聞比打壓</span><br />\n<br />\n通訊辦周六至今收200多宗涉及港台《頭條新聞》投訴<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509177-20200218.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509177-20200218.htm&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=27ffec2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509177-20200218.htm&h=324462f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509177-20200218.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】通訊辦收逾200個涉《頭條新聞》投訴 藍絲狙擊港台以「黑警」相稱<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200218/7QKBFKOCRQFVIYV2YAIIHGI6QI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200218%2F7QKBFKOCRQFVIYV2YAIIHGI6QI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=a408993e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200218%2F7QKBFKOCRQFVIYV2YAIIHGI6QI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=5c349c2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200218/7QKBFKOCRQFVIYV2YAIIHGI6QI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n&ldquo;有市民亦不滿警隊及藍絲陣營容不下批評，呼籲市民一人一電郵支持《頭條新聞》節目，強調郵件必須同時發送至港台（　ccu@rthk.hk ）、商經局（ ccibenq@cedb.gov.hk ）及梁家榮（ kwleung@rthk.hk ）。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"9c6cd23ad8b8ffcb02a5d47ac4a956844095c2a2","tid":1886130,"uid":185424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T17:59:32.000Z","msg":"寫左laaa"},{"pid":"563e0711ccc3e635b8bfa5cf2fd7d9551ec1c41d","tid":1886130,"uid":45301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T18:02:49.000Z","msg":"寫左"},{"pid":"16fce9107bbfd9ea01701851ea42249a310fb67d","tid":1886130,"uid":279887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T18:10:35.000Z","msg":"寫左了"},{"pid":"d252ec260cd639edf0729e950f7ac43fa60c26a4","tid":1886130,"uid":291284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T18:11:00.000Z","msg":"1封"},{"pid":"a0cc7bba243fc2ad2b208f2a11bdb75578943d4e","tid":1886130,"uid":42355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T18:14:27.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n寫讚揚信呀各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65bc93fbbe3a36bf4fd9077e0b0891c17d53dc0","tid":1886130,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T18:15:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c4a6634f46908014a4f590e30720b2d3883be11","tid":1886130,"uid":229615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T18:15:46.000Z","msg":"寫左比署長"},{"pid":"bb3dcf1dc0169904463563405aae5bbc46bcfd23","tid":1886130,"uid":30481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T18:15:46.000Z","msg":"寫咗"},{"pid":"95b7abb763b577922ed1028a6012db8104c1a3a6","tid":1886130,"uid":51677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T18:15:49.000Z","msg":"寫左"},{"pid":"cf9f2721b85deabcad0d8498943a97c8bcee875d","tid":1886130,"uid":134744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T18:18:34.000Z","msg":"寫左啦<br />\n您好:<br />\n<br />\n本局已經收到你的電郵。如有需要，我們會作出回覆。謝謝。<br />\n鑑於政府部門特別上班安排，以盡量減低疫情在社區傳播的風險，<br />\n我們可能在處理電郵上有所延誤，不便之處，敬請原諒。<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局<br />\n<br />\n(此為電腦自動發出的訊息。)"},{"pid":"24f82967580e407427f4313657687687334267eb","tid":1886130,"uid":87189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T18:21:03.000Z","msg":"Sent"},{"pid":"a421687d193c44b7fc69142f647583038e8fb1c0","tid":1886130,"uid":53149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T18:22:57.000Z","msg":"2封已交，thx"},{"pid":"15a4e226d5e8bec9899bea505948215553e0af9e","tid":1886130,"uid":68589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T18:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />done"},{"pid":"4f13b4db220ce7f72edc2077c13847a4ac24772b","tid":1886130,"uid":103189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T18:27:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"838f527a9d15dd3fc4dcefc60e2dcc68b71dc656","tid":1886130,"uid":320687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:29:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人係劣等民族，沒template係唔會做，麻煩置頂。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n kwleung@rthk.hk<br />\nccibenq@cedb.gov.hk<br />\nccu@rthk.hk<br />\n<br />\n感謝《頭條新聞》兢兢業業反映社會現實<br />\n<br />\n敬啟者：               <br />\n<br />\n一、香港言論自由的空間日益收窄，新聞自由首當其衝，新聞工作者亦要在採訪期間承受更大的人身安全及財產安全的風險。在這樣的時候，香港電台，尤其係 《頭條新聞》一眾監製及製作團隊，仍能秉承多年傳統，不畏政治審查，諷刺時弊，為市民發聲實在難能可貴，本人特致信感謝。<br />\n<br />\n二、對於某政府部門對《頭條新聞》的指責，本人在一番審視之後，發現《頭條新聞》 並沒有做出虛假陳述，而指責者亦都無法舉出任何與節目內容相悖的事實，實在是污衊之舉，本人深感不忿。希望閣下明鑒，不要讓少數信口雌黃的污衊之舉得逞，自掘言論自由等核心價值的墳墓。 <br />\n<br />\n三、鑒於近日社會上出現「公營電台要甘當政府喉舌，中共走狗」的言論，本人深表遺憾。本人希望再次重申，公營電台運營資金來自公帑，取之於民，故需要為人民發聲，而不是任何統治階級。香港電台一直以來秉承為市民發聲的職責，兢兢業業， 本人再此致上最誠摯的感謝！<br />\n<br />\n此致<br />\n<br />\n廣播處長 梁家榮先生<br />\n香港電台總監（電視） 陳俊樂先生<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長 邱騰華先生"}]}